{"name":"Background: Listeners","permission":{"default":0,"Ks55FcjZarvIjLAC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You are part of a group of people whose ears are naturally tuned to hear frequencies and volumes beyond the scope of normal human hearing. You can pick up the slightest electrical signal, which is powered by the fact that you live in and around the National Radio Astronomy Observatory in Pocahontas County. Once per day, you climb up the dish of the telescope to listen to the radio waves from the stars. At the end of the meditation, The Interpreter gives a sermon.&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Skill Proficiencies: Choose two from Religion, Percepción, Insight, Pre-War Knowledge, Deception, Persuasion</li>\n<li>Equipment: Listener's Vestments, a Simple Ranged Weapon, a radio and 10 caps.&nbsp;</li>\n<li><strong>Feature: Recall</strong>. Una vez al día ADV para tirada de INT, para recordar información que has oído.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/violet_03.jpg","_id":"kghbEKdOdGkNm8WY"}
{"name":"Background: Enclave","permission":{"default":0,"Ks55FcjZarvIjLAC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>The Enclave consists of the descendents of high ranking members of the American Government before it fell apart. You have hid around the country and secretly tried to re-establish the United States Government since the Great War started. You are highly secretive and have access to defenses and advancements on research.&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Skills: prewar, investigation, deception</li>\n<li>Tools: all vehicles</li>\n<li>Equipment: Enclave Uniform o Pre-War Clothes, 1 pistol or long arm, 3 Prepared Meals y 20 chapas.</li>\n<li>Feature: Authorized Access. You have access to secret bases and locations controlled by the Government.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/red_26.jpg","_id":"huKnynR6RhRFGWAL"}
{"name":"Background: Prisionero","permission":{"default":0,"Ks55FcjZarvIjLAC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Whether you committed a serious crime, a petty crime, or just happened to cross the wrong person at the wrong time, you’ve spent a fair amount of time in some settlement’s or faction’s prison system. Maybe you’re even a repeat offender who has been in and out on a regular basis. You’ve had enough experience to build the skills that you need to make it less likely for you to get caught again.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Skills: Stealth, Sleight of hand, acrobatics</li>\n<li>Tools: Ladrón</li>\n<li>Equipo: Ropas de prisionero, 1 arma improvisada, 1 ganzúa, 5 chapas.</li>\n<li>Feature: Friends in Low Places. Your time behind bars has allowed you to build up a network of criminal associates. You have advantage on any Charisma based checks made when talking to other criminals.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/items/inventory/chain-silver.jpg","_id":"JToBuZMucethLLrn"}
{"name":"Background: Raider","permission":{"default":0,"Ks55FcjZarvIjLAC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Survivors roaming the unforgiving post-apocalyptic wastes work hard to build homes and supplies so that they can live to see the next sunrise. You have a history of roaming with bands of like-minded people who work hard to take the profits of that hard work for yourselves. What’s theirs is now yours because you had the strength to take it by whatever means necessary.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Skills: Deception, Survival, Intimidation</li>\n<li>Tools: pick 1 from demolition o ladrón&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Idioma: raider</li>\n<li>Equipo: Ropas de raider, 1 arma simple, 5 chapas y 1 Molotov.</li>\n<li>Feature: Raider Friend. los raiders te ven como neutral y no te atacan de entrada.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/dnd5e/icons/skills/affliction_18.jpg","_id":"lzxZM7KUTtKj9uLA"}
